This paper deals with the security and privacy aspects of online services, specifically analyzing the risks of password reuse and modification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves data analysis and machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The study also involves user behavior and demographics, which could be relevant to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper involves building a guessing algorithm, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
